Description:
As you follow along the subterranean river's upper path, you notice sprawling supply caches and splintered chests. From their midst radiates an intense light that reveals itself to be a sad pixie, beckoning to you from inside a magical cage. 

"Help! Let me out! I'll make it worth your while!"
DescriptionAction: What will be the pixie's fate?
